els-diamondback.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10102504/kids-bike-24-inch-wheels-diamondback.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10102504/kids-bike-24-inch-wheels-diamondback-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10102504/kids-bike-24-inch-wheels-diamondback-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10102504/kids-bike-24-inch-wheels-diamondback-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10102504/kids-bike-24-inch-wheels-diamondback-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10102504/kids-bike-24-inch-wheels-diamondback-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10102504/kids-bike-24-inch-wheels-diamondback-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10102504/kids-bike-24-inch-wheels-diamondback-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The Diamondback Metric 24 gets a grip shift; the 1 x 7 speed Shimano Revo drivetrain will keep gear changes simple for young riders who are still figuring out how to “make it harder” and how to “make it easier”.&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10102420/diamondback-metric-24-kids-bike-padded-saddle.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10102420/diamondback-metric-24-kids-bike-padded-saddle.jpg\" alt=\"diamonback metric 24&quot; kids bike padded junior saddle\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.c